<DocsPageLead>
    List groups are a flexible and powerful component for displaying a series of content.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    List groups are a flexible and powerful component for displaying a series of content.
    Modify and extend them to support just about any content within.
</DocsPageParagraph>

